{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c5650201-ab58-5c63-93c4-a9cf0fecfa09","excerpt":"Logo 取自 斜坡上的藝術節 粉絲團 在幾年前在 YouTube…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/isenasenai/\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 logo\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 logo\"\n        src=\"/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 180w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 360w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 720w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/72109/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 1080w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/182ac/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 1440w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/c5abd/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 1930w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>Logo 取自<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/isenasenai/\">斜坡上的藝術節</a>粉絲團</p>\n<hr>\n<p>在幾年前在 YouTube 上亂晃發現了<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jb243ol_cCs\">嵐馨樂團</a>，一聽就被圈粉，原住民的幽默發揮的淋漓盡致，音樂又好聽。然後從而認識屏東在地的<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=59SKNU3-X7s\">小魯凱音樂傳創隊</a>，還有一直重複聽不膩的「<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RJMVsRBLytg\">阿佬啦</a>」樂團。</p>\n<p>前幾年就有注意到斜坡上系列的活動，但一直沒有行動力去參加… (明明那時候人就在屏東)，都是事後才看 YouTube 過過乾癮。這次在週四下午看到 FB 上有人分享，晚上就決定週五請假半天去修了很久發不太動的車然後直接殺過去林後四林參加。</p>\n<hr>\n<h3>高雄修車準備往屏東出發！</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 0\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 0\"\n        src=\"/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg 180w,\n/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg 360w,\n/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg 720w,\n/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/72109/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg 1080w,\n/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/182ac/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg 1440w,\n/static/19add9ae1ed97e965b4b9e3487744954/0d527/kacalisian-2019-0.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>大概 17:40 到了林後四林，從停車場看起來很熱鬧</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 1\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 1\"\n        src=\"/static/d483ff22ad27a76a057d758169e16fba/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d483ff22ad27a76a057d758169e16fba/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-1.jpg 180w,\n/static/d483ff22ad27a76a057d758169e16fba/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-1.jpg 360w,\n/static/d483ff22ad27a76a057d758169e16fba/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-1.jpg 720w,\n/static/d483ff22ad27a76a057d758169e16fba/72109/kacalisian-2019-1.jpg 1080w,\n/static/d483ff22ad27a76a057d758169e16fba/92a9d/kacalisian-2019-1.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"斜坡上的藝術節 2019","date":"November 04, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/kacalisian-2019/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/github-slang/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TL;DR? LGTM? 什麼意思？"}},"next":null}}